dct_title_s: Denny's pocket map of Monterey County, California
dct_alternative_sm: Denny's pocket map of Monterey County, California showing townships, sections, roads, railroads, trails, etc
Pocket map of Monterey County, California
dct_description_sm: by Edward Denny & Co., map publishers.
Relief shown by contour lines and hachures.
Blue line print shows ranchos, townships, wagon roads, railroads, trails, forest reserves, etc.
